targets.rawQuery:
SELECT COUNT (DISTINCT(cmcd_session_id)) AS Plays
FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
      AND cmcd_session_id is not NULL
      AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
      AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
      AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
      AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
      AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})

panels.description: Calculated as percentage of requests signalling rebuffering (CMCD bs) to the total number of requests.

FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
      AND cmcd_session_id is not NULL
      AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
      AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
      AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
      AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
      AND x_edge_detailed_result_type IN (${result_type:singlequote})
      AND cs_protocol_version IN (${protocol_version:singlequote})
      AND cs_protocol IN (${protocol:singlequote})
      AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})

panels.description: Average Play duration estimated from the sum of all video or video/audio objects duration

targets.rawQuery:
WITH CTE AS (
      SELECT SUM(cmcd_object_duration) as duration, cmcd_session_id
      FROM "cmcd-db"."cmcd-table"
      WHERE $__timeFilter
            AND cmcd_session_id is not NULL
            AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
            AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
            AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
            AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
            AND (cmcd_object_type = 'v' OR cmcd_object_type = 'av')
            AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
      GROUP BY cmcd_session_id
) 
SELECT AVG(duration)
FROM CTE

panels.title: Average Play duration

targets.rawQuery:
SELECT AVG(cmcd_measured_throughput)
FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
      AND cmcd_measured_throughput is not NULL
      AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
      AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
      AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
      AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
      AND x_edge_detailed_result_type IN (${result_type:singlequote})
      AND cs_protocol_version IN (${protocol_version:singlequote})
      AND cs_protocol IN (${protocol:singlequote})
      AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT cmcd_session_id) AS Plays, cmcd_streaming_format AS streaming_format
    FROM $__database.$__table
    WHERE $__timeFilter
          AND cmcd_streaming_format IN ('d','h','s','o')
          AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
          AND 'true' in (${device:csv})
          AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
          AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
    GROUP BY cmcd_streaming_format

WITH binned_query AS (
    SELECT c_country as Country, BIN(time, ${interval}) AS bin_time, approx_percentile(cmcd_buffer_length, $percentile * 0.01) as buff_length
    FROM $__database.$__table
    WHERE $__timeFilter
        AND cmcd_buffer_length is not Null
        AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
        AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
        AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
        AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
        AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
    GROUP BY c_country, BIN(time, ${interval})
    ORDER BY bin_time
)
SELECT CREATE_TIME_SERIES(bin_time, buff_length) as Buffer_Length, Country
FROM binned_query
GROUP BY Country

WITH binned_query AS (
    SELECT BIN(time, ${interval}) AS bin_time
           ,approx_percentile(cmcd_measured_throughput, $percentile * 0.01) AS tput
          ,cmcd_object_type
    FROM $__database.$__table
    WHERE $__timeFilter
          AND cmcd_measured_throughput is not Null
          AND cmcd_object_type is not Null
          AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
          AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
          AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
          AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
          AND x_edge_detailed_result_type IN (${result_type:singlequote})
          AND cs_protocol_version IN (${protocol_version:singlequote})
          AND cs_protocol IN (${protocol:singlequote})
          AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
GROUP BY cmcd_object_type, BIN(time, ${interval})
ORDER BY bin_time DESC
)
SELECT CREATE_TIME_SERIES(bin_time, tput) as Measured_Throughput, cmcd_object_type
FROM binned_query
GROUP BY cmcd_object_type

WITH binned_query AS (
    SELECT c_country AS Country, BIN(time, ${interval}) AS bin_time, 
    COUNT (CASE WHEN cmcd_buffer_starvation = true THEN 1 ELSE Null END) as bs
    FROM $__database.$__table
    WHERE $__timeFilter
          AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
          AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
          AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
          AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
          AND x_edge_detailed_result_type IN (${result_type:singlequote})
          AND cs_protocol_version IN (${protocol_version:singlequote})
          AND cs_protocol IN (${protocol:singlequote})
          AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
GROUP BY c_country, BIN(time, ${interval})
ORDER BY bin_time DESC
)
SELECT CREATE_TIME_SERIES(bin_time, bs) as Buffer_Starvation, Country
FROM binned_query
GROUP BY Country

panels.description: Total throughput as estimated from amount of bytes sent to the viewers.

targets.rawQuery:
WITH binned_query AS (  
        SELECT BIN(time, 1s) AS bin_time, sum(sc_bytes) * 1.0 as Bytes_Downloaded
        FROM $__database.$__table
        WHERE $__timeFilter
                AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
                AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
                AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
                AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})         
GROUP BY BIN(time, 1s)
)

SELECT bin_time, (Bytes_Downloaded * 8 / 1048576)  as Throughput
FROM binned_query
ORDER BY bin_time DESC

panels.title: Total Throughput

panels.description: Total throughput as measured by client devices.

targets.rawQuery:
WITH binned_query AS (
      SELECT BIN(time, 1s) AS bin_time, avg(cmcd_measured_throughput) as measured_tput, cmcd_session_id
      FROM $__database.$__table
      WHERE $__timeFilter
            AND cmcd_measured_throughput is NOT NULL
            AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
            AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
            AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
            AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
            AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
      GROUP BY BIN(time, 1s), cmcd_session_id
)

SELECT bin_time, sum(measured_tput) as measured_tput_total
FROM binned_query
GROUP BY bin_time
ORDER BY bin_time DESC

panels.title: Total Measured Throughput

targets.rawQuery:
SELECT BIN(time, 1s) AS bin_time, COUNT(x_edge_request_id) AS Requests
FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
      AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
      AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
      AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
      AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
GROUP BY BIN(time, 1s)
ORDER BY BIN(time, 1s) DESC

WITH binned_query AS (
SELECT BIN(time, ${interval}) AS bin_time, sum(sc_bytes) * 1.0 as Bytes_Downloaded
FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
      AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
      AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
      AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
      AND x_edge_response_result_type in ('Miss', 'PrefetchMiss', 'RefreshHit')
      AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
GROUP BY BIN(time, ${interval})
)
SELECT bin_time, (Bytes_Downloaded * 8 / 1048576) / 60 as Throughput
FROM binned_query
ORDER BY bin_time DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(cmcd_session_id)) as Plays, c_country as Country
FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
--      AND c_country != '-'
        AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
        AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
        AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
        AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
GROUP BY c_country

WITH CTE as (
      SELECT regexp_extract(x_edge_location, '([A-Z]{3}).*', 1) as PoP
             ,COUNT(DISTINCT(cmcd_session_id)) as CNT
      FROM $__database.$__table
      WHERE $__timeFilter
            AND cmcd_session_id is not Null
            AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
            AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
            AND cmcd_streaming_format IN (${streaming_format:singlequote})
            AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
      GROUP BY x_edge_location
)
SELECT sum(CNT), PoP
FROM CTE
GROUP BY PoP

SELECT count_if (x_edge_response_result_type = 'Hit') / (1.0 * count (x_edge_request_id)) * 100 AS chr
     ,BIN(time, ${interval})
FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
     AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
     AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
     AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
     AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
GROUP BY BIN(time, ${interval})
ORDER BY BIN(time, ${interval}) DESC

WITH binned_query AS (
SELECT x_edge_location AS Edge, BIN(time, ${interval}) AS bin_time, sum(sc_bytes) AS Bytes
FROM $__database.$__table
WHERE $__timeFilter
      AND c_country IN (${country:singlequote})
      AND 'true' IN (${device:csv})
      AND x_host_header IN (${distribution:singlequote})
      AND COALESCE (asn, '') IN (${asn:singlequote})
GROUP BY x_edge_location, BIN(time, ${interval})
order by bin_time DESC
)
SELECT Edge, CREATE_TIME_SERIES(bin_time, Bytes) AS Bytes_Downloaded
FROM binned_query
GROUP BY Edge
